    <item>
      <title>智利通胀加速，引发降息谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/chile-prices-rise-more-than-forecast-amid-caution-on-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利上个月消费者价格涨幅超出预期，突显出央行在过去一年带头拉美降息后，对进一步降息持谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/chile-prices-rise-more-than-forecast-amid-caution-on-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 12:20:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BBVA 告诉萨瓦德尔，“没有空间”改进报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/bbva-chairman-told-sabadell-there-s-no-room-for-improved-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毕尔巴鄂比斯开银行 (Banco Bilbao Vizcaya Argentaria SA) 董事长告诉萨瓦德尔银行 (Banco Sabadell SA) 的同行，该银行“没有空间”改进其拟议的收购要约，部分原因是其收购消息传出后，该银行股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/bbva-chairman-told-sabadell-there-s-no-room-for-improved-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 07:44:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富时 100 实时指数：指数再创新高，英镑下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2024-05-08/what-s-moving-uk-markets-right-now-markets-today</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年 4 月 23 日星期二，伦敦证券交易所集团有限公司标志显示在英国伦敦市公司办公室中庭的板上。4 月 21 日星期一，富时 100 指数收盘创下历史新高。由于近期股市波动和地缘政治风险促使投资者纷纷涌入英国基准指数的防御性板块，这是一年多以来的首次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2024-05-08/what-s-moving-uk-markets-right-now-markets-today</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 05:52:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果英国央行在资产出售方面发生转变，亨特可能会获得 100 亿英镑的减税净额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/boe-shift-on-quantitative-easing-could-save-uk-government-10-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据英国央行披露，如果英国央行停止出售十多年来在量化宽松政策下购买的债券，英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特每年将额外获得 100 亿英镑的减税资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/boe-shift-on-quantitative-easing-could-save-uk-government-10-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
